---
---

<section
  id="about"
  class="border-t border-slate-200/90 bg-white py-24 sm:py-28"
  aria-labelledby="about-heading"
>
  <div class="page-shell">
    <div class="max-w-full">
      <p class="text-xs font-bold font-label uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-sea">About</p>
      <h2
        id="about-heading"
        class="mt-3 whitespace-nowrap text-[clamp(2rem,3.2vw,3.2rem)] font-semibold leading-tight text-ink"
      >
        By Students, For Students
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="relative mt-12 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#a8c8ff] via-[#94bbff] to-[#82adff] p-8 md:p-12 lg:p-14">
      <div
        class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-white/12"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>
      <div
        class="pointer-events-none absolute -left-12 -top-16 h-56 w-56 rounded-full bg-white/38 blur-3xl"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>
      <div
        class="pointer-events-none absolute -right-10 bottom-0 h-60 w-60 rounded-full bg-[#6ea0ff]/45 blur-3xl"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>
      <div
        class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 rounded-3xl ring-1 ring-white/35 ring-inset"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>
      <h3
        class="relative text-center text-xl font-extrabold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-white font-alt md:text-2xl"
      >
        Mission Statement
      </h3>
      <p
        class="relative mx-auto mt-6 max-w-4xl text-center text-xl font-alt leading-relaxed text-white md:text-2xl"
      >
        We, as AP Ambassadors, aim to cultivate a culture of excellence through student leaders;
        giving them the space to drive participation and improve performance not only in the
        classroom, but also in the community.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-10">
      <article class="relative z-10 rounded-2xl bg-[#f0f2f8] p-8 lg:p-10 before:absolute before:-inset-1.5 before:-z-10 before:rounded-[1.1rem] before:border before:border-slate-300/70">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold italic uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-ink">Who we are</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink/75 lg:text-base">
          The Denmark High School AP Ambassador program is comprised of ~20 current sophomores,
          juniors, and seniors, with the exception of one freshman nominated by their AP Human
          Geography teacher halfway through their freshman year.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="relative z-10 rounded-2xl bg-[#f0f2f8] p-8 lg:p-10 before:absolute before:-inset-1.5 before:-z-10 before:rounded-[1.1rem] before:border before:border-slate-300/70">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold italic uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-ink">What we do</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink/75 lg:text-base">
          We cultivate a culture of excellence inside and outside the classroom. We strive to
          increase AP participation and performance by encouraging AP studies and bringing a
          diverse group of students to the table so every perspective is heard. We give back to
          Denmark and the surrounding community by planning and hosting events such as freshmen
          orientation, career pathway night, AP Night, Spring Fling, and more.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="relative z-10 rounded-2xl bg-[#f0f2f8] p-8 lg:p-10 before:absolute before:-inset-1.5 before:-z-10 before:rounded-[1.1rem] before:border before:border-slate-300/70">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold italic uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-ink">Why we do it</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink/75 lg:text-base">
          We believe ambassadors should be prepared to make an impact on the people and
          community we serve. We are driven by a mindset of philanthropy—constantly looking for
          ways to improve situations in every aspect of life and give back to our school and the
          community.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
